<div>It consists of</div><div><ul><li>Two&nbsp;hollow D-shaped<b> electrodes</b>&nbsp;in a&nbsp;<b>vacuum chamber</b>.</li><li>With a&nbsp;<b>uniform magnetic field</b>&nbsp;applied perpendicular to the planes of the electrodes.</li><li>And a&nbsp;<b>high-frequency alternating voltage</b>&nbsp;applied between the electrodes.</li></ul></div>